flowchart LR
    MQ[RocketMQ 消息] --> C[Go 订单消费者]

    subgraph TX[PostgreSQL 本地事务]
        I[插入 consumer_inbox]
        R[锁定或创建 reservation]
        O[创建 orders]
        S[条件扣减 sku_inventory]
        D[写 order_items]
        L[写 inventory_ledger]
        U[迁移 reservation 状态]
        B[写 event_outbox]
        I --> R --> O --> S --> D --> L --> U --> B
    end

    C --> TX
    TX --> COMMIT[COMMIT]
    COMMIT --> ACK[ACK RocketMQ]
    COMMIT --> P[Outbox 发布器]
    P --> RMQ[RocketMQ / Redis 状态更新]
